The United States President, Donald Trump, on Wednesday boasted the country reported one million cases of the coronavirus disease (COVID-19) because of the methodology it employed in testing. Trump who was obviously reacting to critics’ comments on the management of the COVID-19 pandemic in the nation posted on his Twitter page; “The only reason the U.S. has reported one million cases of CoronaVirus is that our Testing is sooo much better than any other country in the World. Other countries are way behind us in Testing, and therefore show far fewer cases!” <img class="wp-image-1385444 aligncenter" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trump-1.jpg?resize=640%2C124&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="640" height="124" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trump-1.jpg?resize=300%2C58&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trump-1.jpg?resize=58%2C11&amp;ssl=1 58w, https://i0.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trump-1.jpg?resize=260%2C50&amp;ssl=1 260w, https://i0.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trump-1.jpg?resize=200%2C39&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Trump-1.jpg?w=534&amp;ssl=1 534w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" data-recalc-dims="1" /> A former Democratic presidential candidate and Trump’s major opponent in the 2016 election, Hillary Clinton, had asked: “Where are the damn tests”. Clinton was reacting to an earlier report that a Detroit health care worker dies after being denied coronavirus test 4 times. <img class="wp-image-1385442 aligncenter" src="https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Hillary-Clinton.jpg?resize=576%2C146&#038;ssl=1" alt="" width="576" height="146" srcset="https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Hillary-Clinton.jpg?resize=300%2C76&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i1.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/upload